elements.name: Deseo ingresar a la aplicación, ver la lista de etquetas, Intentar crear una etiqueta con valores vacios y verificar que se muestra el mensaje de err

steps.name: I go to "<GHOST-VERSION-1-URL1>"
I wait for 2 seconds
I enter email "<USERNAME>" into selector "input[name='identification']"
I enter password "<PASSWORD>" into selector "input[name='password']"
I take screenshot of step "1" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_17>" and feature "Tags" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-1>"
I push login button with selector "button[type='submit']"
I wait for 2 seconds
I expect to enter to Ghost home page "<GHOST-VERSION-1-URL2>"
I click on Tags list with selector "a[href='#/tags/']"
I take screenshot of step "2" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_17>" and feature "Tags" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-1>"
I expect to enter to Ghost Tags section "<GHOST-VERSION-1-URL3>"
I wait for 1 seconds
I click on New Tag with selector "a[href='#/tags/new/']"
I wait for 1 seconds
I take screenshot of step "3" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_17>" and feature "Tags" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-1>"
I do not enter Tag Name
I enter Tag Color "CCCCCC" into selector "input[name='accent-color']"
I enter Tag Slug "$name_2" into selector "input[name='slug']"
I enter Tag Description "$string_1" into selector "textarea[name='description']"
I take screenshot of step "4" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_17>" and feature "Tags" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-1>"
I push Save button with selector "button[class='gh-btn gh-btn-blue gh-btn-icon ember-view']"
I wait for 1 seconds
I looking for error "You must specify a name for the tag." on selector "p[class='response']"
I take screenshot of step "5" and scenario "<ESCENARIO_17>" and feature "Tags" and version "<GHOST-VERSION-1>"
I wait for 1 seconds
